== 製作 ==
本片於2014年秋天開始拍攝，分別在兩個大型[[攝影棚|攝影棚]]中建造相關布景<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nextmag.com.tw/realtimenews/news/39545912|title=《魔鏡夢遊：時光怪客》搞穿越　強尼戴普掛病號等救援|author=趙怡華|date=2016-05-28|newspaper=臺灣壹週刊|accessdate=2018-02-03|language=zh-TW}}</ref>。在拍攝技術上本片一改前作的[[綠幕|綠幕]]，而是採用較不刺眼的[[藍幕|藍幕]]，且增加了更多的實體布景<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.mtime.com/2016/05/23/1555662-all.html#p2|title=《爱丽丝梦游仙境2》主创专访 现实or幻想？ 各有解读就是魅力所在|accessdate=2018-02-03|date=2016-05-30|publisher=Mtime时光网|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180204000319/http://news.mtime.com/2016/05/23/1555662-all.html#p2|archive-date=2018-02-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；此外還聘請了著名的電影[[美術指導|美術指導]][[丹·漢納|丹·漢納]]來協助設計本片中的奇幻世界<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.denofgeek.com/us/movies/alice-through-the-looking-glass/255494/alice-through-the-looking-glass-review|title=Alice Through the Looking Glass Review|newspaper=Den of Geek|accessdate=2018-02-03|language=en}}</ref>。

==反響==
===專業評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度僅29%，基於248條評論，平均分為4.57/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/alice_in_wonderland_through_the_looking_glass/ |title=Alice Through the Looking Glass (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=May 28, 2016}}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分34，[[IMDB|IMDB]]得6.4。普遍不受影評人認同<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/alice-through-the-looking-glass |title=Alice Through the Looking Glass reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=May 27, 2016}}</ref>。相反地，據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，在A+至F間觀眾的評價平均落在「A-」，和前集同分<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/x-men-apocalypse-alice-through-the-looking-glass-memorial-day-weekend-box-office-1201763668/ |title=‘X-Men: Apocalypse’ Firing Off $90M, ‘Alice’ Taking A Spill With $40M Over 4-Day Memorial Day Holiday |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-05-28 |archive-date=2016-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160528142124/http://deadline.com/2016/05/x-men-apocalypse-alice-through-the-looking-glass-memorial-day-weekend-box-office-1201763668/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
美國首映週末票房僅2810萬美元，次于《[[X戰警：天啟|X戰警：天啟]]》列第二位，比前集的1.16億美元下跌了70%，口碑悽慘<ref name="THRweeknd">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-x-men-apocalypse-898171|title=Box Office: 'X-Men: Apocalypse' No. 1 With $80M; 'Alice Through the Looking Glass' Bombs|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=May 29, 2016|accessdate=May 29, 2016|archive-date=2016-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530122504/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-x-men-apocalypse-898171|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中国大陆首周3天取得1.76亿人民币居冠，最终成绩3.86亿。

